First Ave., west side, north from East 108th Street. Storage tanks of the Consolidated Gas Co., are between 110th and 111th Streets. Wine equipment shown in the foreground, is outside of store at No. 2060, between 106th and 107th Streets.

October 1930.

P. L. Sperr.

(1)
First Avenue, west side, from 108th to 110th Streets, inclusive. The building on the S.W. corner of 108th Street is fairly new, since 1925.
May 23, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, not showing the new building on the S.W. corner of 108th Street.
May 23, 1934.
